Lani Minella https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lani_Minella 0 Lani Minella (born July 28, 1950) is an American actress, director, and producer mostly working in the gaming industry. She is also the founder and owner of the voice-acting agency, AudioGodz. Lani_Minella ( born July_28_,_1950 ) is an_American_actress , director , and producer mostly_working in the_gaming_industry .
